DAX Formula 8

Load all this DAX formulas before going to the next step.

Measures and calculated columns added

 

1)  .%1weekEndP = IFERROR(([.0test]-[.0test2])/[.0test2],"Finished")

 

2)  .%2weekEndP = IFERROR(([.0test2]-[.Last2weekFinalStudent])/[.Last2weekFinalStudent],"Finished")

 

3)  .0011 = if(Count(ClassRetention[WkDiff])<>15,[.%1weekEndP])

 

4)  .0EndP1week = var Maxweek= If(CALCULATE(max(ClassRetention[WkDiff])-1, ALLEXCEPT(ClassRetention, ClassRetention[ClassName])) = MAX (ClassRetention[WkDiff]),1,0)*AVERAGE(ClassRetention[WkDiff]) return CALCULATE(sum(ClassRetention[EndP]),ClassRetention[WkDiff]=Maxweek)

 

5)  .0EndStudent1WeekAgo = sumx(ClassRetention,[.0EndP1week])

 

6)  .0KPIArrow = IFERROR(SWITCH(true(),[.1DropOutKPI]>[.2DropOutKpi],UNICHAR(9650), [.1DropOutKPI]<[.2DropOutKpi],UNICHAR(9660),[.1DropOutKPI]=[.2DropOutKpi],""),"N/A")

 

7)  .0KPIArrowColor = Switch(true() ,[.1DropOutKPI]>1,"#b3b3b3",[.1DropOutKPI]<= [.2DropOutKpi], "#22BC22",[.1DropOutKPI]>[.2DropOutKpi],"#ff0038")

 

8)  .0test = If(count(ClassRetention[WkDiff])<>15, CALCULATE([.Student_dropout1],FILTER(ClassRetention,ClassRetention[WkDiff]>2 && ClassRetention[WkDiff]<15 )),0)

 

9)  .0test2 = If(COUNT(ClassRetention[WkDiff])<>15,CALCULATE([.LastweekFinalStudent], FILTER(ClassRetention,ClassRetention[WkDiff]>1 && ClassRetention[WkDiff]<14)),0)

 

10) .1DropOutKPI = IFERROR( -1*([.1EndPD.P]-[.2EndPD.P])/[.2EndPD.P], "Finished")

 

11) .1EndDpColorcode = If([.1DropOutKPI]>1,"#b3b3b3")

 

12) .1EndDpColorcode = If([.1DropOutKPI]>1,"#b3b3b3")

 

13) .1Logicchecklist = CALCULATE([.FinalStudent],FILTER(ClassRetention,If( sumx(ClassRetention,If(AVERAGE(ClassRetention[EndP])>=1,1,0))>2,1)))

 

 

14) .1Logichecklistsumx = If(Sumx(ClassRetention,[.1Logicchecklist])>=3, [.1Logicchecklist])*[.FinalStudent]

 

15) .2Daxforfinal = var Maxweek= If(CALCULATE(max(ClassRetention[WkDiff]), ALLEXCEPT(ClassRetention, ClassRetention[ClassName])) = MAX (ClassRetention[WkDiff]),1,0)*AVERAGE(ClassRetention[WkDiff]) return CALCULATE(sum(ClassRetention[EndP]),ClassRetention[WkDiff]=Maxweek)

 

 

16) .2DropOutKpi = IFERROR(-1*([.2EndPD.P]-[.3_EndStudentLastweek])/[.3_EndStudentLastweek],"Finished")

 

 

17) .2EndPD.P = If(COUNT(ClassRetention[WkDiff])<>15,CALCULATE([.0EndStudent1WeekAgo], FILTER(ClassRetention,ClassRetention[WkDiff]>1 && ClassRetention[WkDiff]<14)),0)

 

 

18) .3_EndStudentLastweek = If( COUNT(ClassRetention[WkDiff])<>15,CALCULATE((sumx (ClassRetention, [.3EndStudent])),FILTER(ClassRetention,ClassRetention[WkDiff]<13)))

 

 

19) .3Daxfornewstud = var Maxweek= If(CALCULATE(max(ClassRetention[WkDiff]), ALLEXCEPT(ClassRetention, ClassRetention[ClassName])) = MAX (ClassRetention[WkDiff]),1,0)*AVERAGE(ClassRetention[WkDiff]) return CALCULATE(sum(ClassRetention[NewP]),ClassRetention[WkDiff]=Maxweek)

 

 

20) .3EndStudent = sumx(ClassRetention,var Maxweek= If(CALCULATE(max(ClassRetention[WkDiff])-2, ALLEXCEPT(ClassRetention, ClassRetention[ClassName])) = MAX (ClassRetention[WkDiff]),1,0)*AVERAGE(ClassRetention[WkDiff]) return CALCULATE(sum(ClassRetention[EndP]),ClassRetention[WkDiff]=Maxweek))

 

 

21) .4Daxforstartst = var Maxweek= If(CALCULATE(max(ClassRetention[WkDiff]), ALLEXCEPT(ClassRetention, ClassRetention[ClassName])) = MAX (ClassRetention[WkDiff]),1,0)*AVERAGE(ClassRetention[WkDiff]) return CALCULATE(sum(ClassRetention[StartP]),ClassRetention[WkDiff]=Maxweek)

 

 

22) .Color KPI = SWITCH(TRUE (), [.Indicator]>0.9,1,[.Indicator]>0.8,2,[.Indicator] >0.62,3,[.Indicator]>0.35,4,5)

 

 

23) .ColorKPIDropRate = SWITCH(TRUE (), [.TotalDrop]=1,1,[.TotalDrop]=2,2,[.TotalDrop]=3,3,[.TotalDrop]=3,4,5)

 

24) .DifferenceAVGE = var MaxWEEK = MIN(ClassRetention[Week Diffrence])+1 var MinWeek= MIN(ClassRetention[Week Diffrence])                                                  RETURN if (CALCULATE(SUM(ClassRetention[RetentionRate]) ,ClassRetention[Week Diffrence]=MaxWEEK)<>0,CALCULATE(SUM(ClassRetention[RetentionRate]),ClassRetention[Week Diffrence]=MaxWEEK) - CALCULATE(SUM(ClassRetention[RetentionRate]),ClassRetention[Week Diffrence]=MinWeek))

 

25) .FinalDropOut = sumx(ClassRetention,[.Student_dropout1])

 

26) .FinalStudent = sumx(ClassRetention,[.2Daxforfinal])

 

27) .GradColorcode = SWITCH(true(),[.GraduateStud]>=0.75 && [.GraduateStud]<=1, "#3BBD33",[.GraduateStud]<0.75,"#ff0000",[.GraduateStud]>1,"#B3B3B3")

 

 

28) .GraduateStud = If((CALCULATE(sum(ClassRetention[EndP]),ClassRetention[WkDiff] =15))/(CALCULATE(sum(ClassRetention[StartP]),ClassRetention[WkDiff]=15)+CALCULATE(sum(ClassRetention[NewP]),ClassRetention[WkDiff]=15))=BLANK(),"Incomplete",(CALCULATE(sum(ClassRetention[EndP]),ClassRetention[WkDiff]=15))/(CALCULATE(sum(ClassRetention[StartP]),ClassRetention[WkDiff]=15)+CALCULATE(sum(ClassRetention[NewP]),ClassRetention[WkDiff]=15)))

 

29) .Indicator = SUM(ClassRetention[RetentionRate])/COUNT(ClassRetention[RetentionRate])

 

30) .KPI GREEN = IF( [.Indicator]> [.MAXRate],1,2)

 

31) .KPI RED = IF([.Indicator]< [.MINRate],1,0)

 

32) .KPI YELLOW = if([.Indicator] <= [.MAXRate] && [.Indicator]>=[.MINRate] ,1,0)

 

33) .Last2weekdropstudent = var Maxweek= If(CALCULATE(max(ClassRetention[WkDiff])-2, ALLEXCEPT(ClassRetention, ClassRetention[ClassName])) = MAX (ClassRetention[WkDiff]),1,0)*AVERAGE(ClassRetention[WkDiff]) return CALCULATE((sum(ClassRetention[StartP])+sum(ClassRetention[NewP]))-sum(ClassRetention[EndP]),ClassRetention[WkDiff]=Maxweek)

 

 

34) .Last2weekFinalStudent = If( COUNT(ClassRetention[WkDiff])<>15,CALCULATE((sumx (ClassRetention,[.Last2weekdropstudent])),FILTER(ClassRetention,ClassRetention[WkDiff]<13)))

 

 

35) .LastweekFinalStudent = sumx(ClassRetention,var Maxweek= If(CALCULATE(max(ClassRetention[WkDiff])-1, ALLEXCEPT(ClassRetention, ClassRetention[ClassName])) = MAX (ClassRetention[WkDiff]),1,0)*AVERAGE(ClassRetention[WkDiff]) return CALCULATE(((sum(ClassRetention[StartP])+sum(ClassRetention[NewP]))-sum(ClassRetention[EndP])),ClassRetention[WkDiff]=Maxweek))

 

36) .Logicalfinalstudent = If(If(COUNTX(ClassRetention,ClassRetention[WkDiff]) >2=TRUE(),1,0)>=1,1)

 

37) .MAXClassRetention = MAX(ClassRetention[RetentionRate])

 

38) .MAXRate = 0.80

 

39) .MINRate = 0.74

 

40) .MINRetationRate = MIN(ClassRetention[RetentionRate])

 

41) .NwWeek = If([.DifferenceAVGE]<>0,[.DifferenceAVGE])

 

42) .Student_dropout1 = [.Target_Student]-[.FinalStudent]

 

43) .SumNewp = sumx(ClassRetention,[.3Daxfornewstud])

 

44) .SumStartP = sumx(ClassRetention,[.4Daxforstartst])

 

45) .Target_Student = Sumx(ClassRetention,[.SumNewp]+[.SumStartP])

 

 

46) .test2 = CALCULATE([.LastweekFinalStudent],FILTER(ClassRetention, ClassRetention[WkDiff]>2))

 

 

47) .TotalDrop = If ([.WeeklyDifdropout] <>0 , [.WeeklyDifdropout])

 

48) .WeeklyDifdropout = var MaxWEEK = MIN(ClassRetention[Week Diffrence])+1 var MinWeek= MIN(ClassRetention[Week Diffrence]) RETURN if (CALCULATE(SUM(ClassRetention[dropout]),ClassRetention[Week Diffrence]=MaxWEEK)<>0,CALCULATE(SUM(ClassRetention[dropout]),ClassRetention[Week Diffrence]=MaxWEEK) - CALCULATE(SUM(ClassRetention[dropout]),ClassRetention[Week Diffrence]=MinWeek))

 

49) NewWeek = If( [.DifferenceAVGE]>0,1)

 

51) .1EndPD.P = If(count(ClassRetention[WkDiff])<>15, CALCULATE([.FinalStudent],FILTER(ClassRetention,ClassRetention[WkDiff]>2 && ClassRetention[WkDiff]<15 )),0) 

*******************Columns and functions

50 dropout = (ClassRetention[StartP]+ClassRetention[NewP])- ClassRetention[EndP]
